    ComputerSystemPanel
    A component that contains workspace for creating and editing graph of the computer system.

    A component of the console.

    This class encapsulates methods to print console information messages.
    GraphGeneratorPanel
    A component, which contains random graphs generation tools.
    GraphPanel  
    MainFrame
    Main component, on which other components are located.
    RandomGraphPanel
    This component is used to graphically display randomly generated task graphs.
    SchedulePanel
    This component graphically displays schedule diagram, which is based on the task graph, computer system topology and specified parameters(algorithm type, links number etc.).
